channel.title: Aws ami images does not seem to work
channel.description: I follow the steps in https://redash.io/help/open-source/setup#aws including opening inbound traffic on 22, 80 and 443 but when the instance is up and I point my browser to its ip I get no response. What am I missing?

item.title: Aws ami images does not seem to work
item.dc:creator: griffinator76
item.description:
Does your instance have a public IP address? If not it will not be reachable from outside the VPC it was created in.
